<Layout title="AI Search Visibility Audit for Law Firms in Birmingham | Rank4AI" description="Free AI search visibility audit for law firms in Birmingham. Test your firm across ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, Perplexity, Copilot and Google AI Overviews. Delivered in five working days by Rank4AI.">

<SpeakableSchema
